---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Spot Guides - Surf Deeper" description="Discover surf spots with maps, local insights, tide charts, and hazards contributed by the community.">
  <header class="page-header">
    <h1>Spot Guides</h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle">Discover waves around the world</p>
  </header>

  <section class="spot-features">
    <h2>What You'll Find</h2>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>Interactive Maps</h3>
        <p>Detailed maps showing break locations, access points, and parking areas</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>Wave Information</h3>
        <p>Wave type, size, direction, and best conditions for each spot</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>Tide Charts</h3>
        <p>Local tide information and how it affects wave quality</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Hazards & Safety</h3>
        <p>Important safety information, hazards, and local knowledge</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>Local Insights</h3>
        <p>Tips from locals about crowd levels, best times, and etiquette</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>Photos & Videos</h3>
        <p>Visual guides showing the break in different conditions</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="spot-categories">
    <h2>Browse by Region</h2>
    <div class="region-grid">
      <div class="region-card">
        <h3>California</h3>
        <p>From Malibu to Mavericks</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/spots/linda-mar">Linda Mar Beach</a></li>
          <li>Los Angeles County</li>
          <li>Orange County</li>
          <li>San Diego</li>
          <li>Central Coast</li>
          <li>Northern California</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="region-card">
        <h3>Hawaii</h3>
        <p>The birthplace of surfing</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Oahu</li>
          <li>Maui</li>
          <li>Kauai</li>
          <li>Big Island</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="region-card">
        <h3>Australia</h3>
        <p>World-class waves down under</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Gold Coast</li>
          <li>Byron Bay</li>
          <li>Bells Beach</li>
          <li>Margaret River</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="region-card">
        <h3>Europe</h3>
        <p>Cold water perfection</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Portugal</li>
          <li>Spain</li>
          <li>France</li>
          <li>Ireland</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="coming-soon">
    <h2>Coming Soon</h2>
    <p>We're building a comprehensive database of surf spots with detailed information contributed by the community. Each spot guide will include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>üìç Precise location and access information</li>
      <li>üåä Wave characteristics and best conditions</li>
      <li>üåÖ Tide and wind dependencies</li>
      <li>‚ö†Ô∏è Safety considerations and hazards</li>
      <li>üë• Local etiquette and crowd information</li>
      <li>üì∏ Photos and videos from the community</li>
      <li>üí¨ Reviews and tips from surfers</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="contribute-cta">
    <h2>Share Your Local Knowledge</h2>
    <p>Know a great surf spot? Help the community by sharing your local knowledge and insights.</p>
    <a href="/contribute" class="cta-button">Add a Spot Guide</a>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #00ff88;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .spot-features h2,
  .spot-categories h2 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #00ff88;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background-color: #1e293b;
    border: 2px solid #334155;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    border-color: #00ff88;
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: #00ff88;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .region-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .region-card {
    background-color: #1e293b;
    border: 2px solid #334155;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .region-card:hover {
    border-color: #00ff88;
  }

  .region-card h3 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .region-card p {
    color: #00ff88;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .region-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .region-card li {
    color: #00ff88;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .region-card li::before {
    content: "‚Üí";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #00cc6a;
  }

  .coming-soon {
    background-color: #1e293b;
    border: 2px solid #334155;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .coming-soon h2 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .coming-soon p {
    color: #00ff88;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .coming-soon ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .coming-soon li {
    color: #00ff88;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .contribute-cta {
    text-align: center;
    background-color: #1e293b;
    border: 2px solid #00ff88;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .contribute-cta h2 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .contribute-cta p {
    color: #00ff88;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: #00ff88;
    color: #0f172a;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background-color: #00cc6a;
  }
</style>
